description: Exquisite Views! Stunning 18th floor corner home located at the coveted 1521- Gorgeous views of Elliott Bay, Puget Sound & Olympic Mountains. Expansive walls of glass, soaring 10' ceilings- home is flooded with natural light. Enjoy a unique blend of indoor-outdoor living in the enclosed glass solarium featuring retractable windows. Open-concept layout, gourmet kitchen, solid wood cabinets, top-tier appliance- dream home for entertaining. Enjoy oversized Primary with large walk in closet, spa-inspired bath,heated floors,jetted tub, oversized shower & dual vanities World class location & amenities- 24/7 concierge, rooftop BBQ, gym, yoga studio, conference room & entertaining spaces. Pike Place Market just across the street. 2pk- w/EV charger.
